4149:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_uart.c **** /**
4150:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @brief  Wrap up transmission in non-blocking mode.
